<br>
It's a combination of 2 things, first the fact that monks don't take damage as fast as a warrior. For most &quot;normal&quot; players, this advantage is vastly negated by the hps advantage plate tanks have over monks. You can use more efficient heals, and you have more time to react on a &quot;normal&quot; plate tank. Monks still do fine on most grinds as a tank though - which is fine with me. With intelligent players, any melee can do fine as a tank.<br>
<br>
The big problem is on higher end items being all/all, making the set hps advantage warriors and knights have over monks being a lot less important relatively speaking. <br>
